snippet.title: Computer Diplomacy gameplay (PC Game, 1984)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Computer Diplomacy, Dos PC game produced by Avalon Hill in 1984 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/diplomacy/234/
Computer Diplomacy is a game of strategy, simulation, politics. Choose a country to play as, and attempt world domination.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
